replies.author: xmdhs
replies.txt_content:
你可以试试我打包好的 https://pan.baidu.com/s/1c990HMfoi9-AhY_wm4nE6A

或者更新启动器，https://ci.huangyuhui.net/job/HM ... bs/HMCL-3.2.147.exe

然后启动器设置，下载源，mcbbs 

然后尝试安装
